            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-10-15T17:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-07-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="170" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d170">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.F.1.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 71</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>The Canadian Delegation proposes that Article 71 of the Draft Peace Treaty with
                    Italy be amended as follows:</p>
                <p>The words “18 months” in the second line of the first paragraph of this Article
                    be deleted and the words “3 years” substituted therefor.</p>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Amendment Proposed by the Delegation of China Peace Treaty
                        With Italy</hi>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
